featured_reviews.review_id: Peaceful but organised. This Masjid is well respected by all communities. It is residential and Zamats from all abroad stay here for weeks. This locality is not densely populated. It is far away from the HQ of Sagar District. Inhabitants are calm and simple. People come here to visit the Beena Water Falls and the Fort. The main business is Bidi making and raw leather exporting.
